PrecisRegulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (MOTORCYCLES AND THREE-WHEELED VEHICLES) AND THE MOTOR VEHICLE TIRE SAFETY REGULATIONS, 1995 by modifying the existing classification definition for motorcycles, introducing a new vehicle class for three-wheeled vehicles and by introducing safety standards addressing fuel system integrity and vehicle stability requirements.
